Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her, I got to try my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I definitely can\Nriddle Germa's modified human bodies with bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy kept fighting\Nin order to wait for Sanji at the rendezvous point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not for you!
